{"tid":364823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓血腥掃毒　3天已擊斃80人","createTime":"2017-08-18T17:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T17:05:40.000Z","uid":37554,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e61154163dbaa0e04310a8ac7d3b54f18ec312e","tid":364823,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"菲律賓總統杜特蒂（Rodrigo Duterte）上任以來血腥掃毒，馬尼拉警方本周二起連續3晚在貧民窟或中低收入階層聚居區域掃蕩可疑毒犯，至昨已擊斃80人。<br />\n路透報導，警方周二、三兩晚在馬尼拉及鄰近省分共擊斃67人，昨晚又擊斃13人。另有逾200人被捕。相關行動引起隸屬反對黨的副總統羅貝多強烈譴責。左翼團體民族運動（Bayan movement）也表示，即使該團體呼籲減少非法毒品，這樣的屠殺行動也必須停止，「必須有長期徹底的解決方案。法西斯式的解決方案註定失敗。」　（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170818/420_cb37c948576ab604bef6c37f30522f98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170818%2F420_cb37c948576ab604bef6c37f30522f98.jpg&h=529515e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170818/420_e44911729ff29c7f05d004e15fc5a476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170818%2F420_e44911729ff29c7f05d004e15fc5a476.jpg&h=a6be2f07&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}